   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Train 30 Teachers and Strengthen Our Communities</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Through the Hermanus Varsity Trust, over the next four years 30 young people will qualify as teachers.  Driven by local professionals who volunteer to tutor the students, this project has two main goals. One is offering young people from poor communities access quality education and good jobs.  The other is to foster teachers who bring passion and excellence to their teaching. Their well-paid employment will contribute to more stable and prosperous communities.</narrative>
  </description>
